metadata.author: Jacqueline Harvey
metadata.description: Join Willa and her loyal dog Woof in two thrilling adventures! First, Willa juggles planning a big event at the retirement village with training for her first gymnastics competition, all while dealing with a bully on the committee. Then, Willa faces school play drama as a new kid disrupts her friendships, and she must pull everything together in time for the big performance.
